Women Consortium of Nigeria (WOCON) bụ òtù na-enweghị uru nke nwere isi na Lagos Nigeria
Ọ bụ onye isi Olabisi Olateru-Olagbegi guzobere ya na 1993 maka ịkwalite ikike ụmụ nwanyị na ụmụaka na Naịjirịa
WOCON duziri mkpọsa megide ịzụ ahịa ụmụ nwanyị na Naịjirịa na 8 Maachị 1996 mgbe nyocha e mere na mbido afọ ahụ na mmekorita ya na United Nations.
